snippet.title: Gisselle's Adventure Oficial Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Through a blend of visual novel, RPG, and platforming elements and after years of homeschooling, Gisselle must face the real world with her social anxiety disorder in a daunting school environment, where every interaction is a battle and every friendship is an achievement.

Available next November 12th 2024 on
-Steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/3196400/Gisselles_Adventure/

-Xbox:https://www.xbox.com/es-mx/games
/store/gisselles-adventure/9npz9cm54mwt



coming soon on playstore
